text: Oberflachs was a municipality of the district of Brugg in the canton of Aargau in Switzerland. On 1 January 2014, the former municipalities of Oberflachs and Schinznach-Dorf merged into the new municipality of Schinznach. ==Other websites== *Official Website of Oberflachs Category:Former municipalities of Aargau
